CONCLUSION: PRODEC addresses the crucial issue of how AI systems could and should inﬂuence requirements and design of sociotechnical systems that support human work, particularly in contexts of high uncertainty. However, PRODEC is still work in progress and advanced visualization techniques and tools are needed to increase physical and ﬁgurative tangibility.},
